Name of the post:

  • Dy Chief Account Officer, Sr Accounts Officer, Assistant Account Officer, Assistant Accountant, Assistant Sales Officer, Assistant Field Officer, Salesman

Description:

The Punjab State Cooperative Supply and Marketing Federation Ltd issued a total of 227 vacancies for the posts of Dy Chief Account Officer, Sr Accounts Officer, Assistant Account Officer, Assistant Accountant, Assistant Sales Officer, Assistant Field Officer, Salesman. The online application for the posts of Dy Chief Account Officer, Sr Accounts Officer, Assistant Account Officer, Assistant Accountant, Assistant Sales Officer, Assistant Field Officer, Salesman under Punjab State Cooperative Supply and Marketing Federation Ltd shall start from 22-03-2021 (11:00 AM). The eligible candidates can apply for the online application before 12-04-2021 up to 05:00 PM. For further detailed information regarding educational qualifications, age limit, selection procedure, for Dy Chief Account Officer, Sr Accounts Officer, Assistant Account Officer, Assistant Accountant, Assistant Sales Officer, Assistant Field Officer, Salesman mentioned below.

. For more such updates do visit theprograd.com .The ProGrad jobs.

 

Mode of application & application fee:

The interested candidates after filling the application form, it is required to pay the application fee to complete the form submission process:

  • Mode of application: Online
  • The application fee for the SC/ ST/ PH is INR 600/-
  • The application fee for the rest of the candidates is INR 1200/-
  • For more details, you can refer to the notification. The link is given at the bottom.

Important dates:

  • The Starting date to apply online is 22-03-2021 (11:00 AM)
  • The Last date to apply online is 20-04-2021 up to 05:00 PM

Age limit criteria:

The interested candidates must have fallen in the age limit criteria provided by the Punjab State Cooperative Supply and Marketing Federation Ltd  is:

  • The minimum age required to apply is 18 Years
  • The maximum age required to apply is 37 Years
  • For age relaxation criteria, you can refer to the notification. The link is given below in The ProGrad jobs.

How to apply for MARKFED, Punjab Various Vacancy Online Form 2021?

  • Note: You can directly apply by clicking apply now button
  • First, visit the official website markfedpunjab.com.
  • Register yourself on the portal of Punjab State Cooperative Supply and Marketing Federation Ltd.
  • Login yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification of Dy Chief Account Officer, Sr Accounts Officer, Assistant Account Officer, Assistant Accountant, Assistant Sales Officer, Assistant Field Officer, Salesman.
  • Fill up the complete details that are asked in the application form.
  • Upload your photo and signature with the dimensions asked in the instructions.
  • Submit the application fee
  • Finally, download the application form for future needs.
